Sentencas: LaCoO3-delta (LC)-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) cathode is fabricated by the solution impregnation method and promoted electrochemical performance is obtained.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ: A promising cathode material with remarkable performance and CO2 resistance for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: After being coated by LC shell, the polarization resistance can be as low as 0.197 Omega cm(2) and the peak power density is 0.243 W cm(-2) at the operating temperature of 600 degrees C.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ: A promising cathode material with remarkable performance and CO2 resistance for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The excellent CO2 resistance of LC-coated BSCF cathode is verified by the CO2-poisoning test.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ: A promising cathode material with remarkable performance and CO2 resistance for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Even in the operating atmosphere with high CO2 concentration, the polarization resistance change of LC-coated BSCF cathode is much smaller than that of the blank BSCF cathode.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ: A promising cathode material with remarkable performance and CO2 resistance for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: By long-term test of single cells, the remarkable electrochemical performance stability of LC-coated BSCF cathode is shown.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ: A promising cathode material with remarkable performance and CO2 resistance for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The promoted electrochemical performance, excellent CO2 resistance and remarkable long-term stability make LC-coated BSCF cathode promising for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ: A promising cathode material with remarkable performance and CO2 resistance for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
